92w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/sinead-o-connor-portrait-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">西妮德·奥康纳</a>的确切死因在她去世一年后才被揭晓。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sinead-oconnor-obituary-3473864">Sinéad O&#39;Connor，1966-2023：一位正直、强烈和诚实的艺术家</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位爱尔兰歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-was-found-unresponsive-at-home-police-say-3474196">于去年7月26日去世，享年56岁，</a>警方发现她在家中失去知觉。去年八月，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-and-bono-among-mourners-at-sinead-oconnors-funeral-3480081">在爱尔兰布雷小镇举行的葬礼上安息</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-geldof">鲍勃·格尔多夫</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bono">波诺</a>也在她的葬礼上表达了哀悼。</p><p>验尸官今年一月证实<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-cause-of-death-confirmed-by-coroner-3567768">奥康纳是自然死亡</a>，但现在她的确切死因已经公布。</p><p>据《 <a href="https://www.independent.ie/irish-news/detail-of-sinead-oconnors-cause-of-death-revealed-on-the-first-anniversary-of-her-passing/a189763303.html"><em>爱尔兰独立报》</em></a>报道，死亡证明（由她的前夫约翰·雷诺兹登记）表明，奥康纳死于慢性阻塞性肺病（COPD）和哮喘。</p><p>该证明还指出，据报道奥康纳还患有“低度呼吸道感染”。伦敦内南区高级验尸官朱利安·莫里斯在未经验尸的情况下完成尸检后证实了这位歌手的死亡。 </p><figure id="attachment_3480013" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3480013" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3480013" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270.jpg" alt="西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinead O&#39;Connor) 登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sinead-OConnor@200-x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3480013" class="wp-caption-text">西妮德·奥康纳在舞台上表演。图片来源：Peter Pakvis/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>自从奥康纳去世后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">Michael Stipe</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-t">Ice-T</a>等人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863#:~:text=She%20dedicated%20the%20award%20for,Roisin%20Waters%20and%20Yeshua%20Bonadio.">纷纷向他表示哀悼</a>。</p><p>比利·柯根最近也公开了他与西妮德·奥康纳的友谊， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-opens-up-about-friendship-with-sinead-oconnor-such-an-incredible-talent-3766023">称赞她是“一位令人难以置信的天才”。</a></p><p> “人们现在意识到我们失去了一个当她在这里时可能应该得到更多关注和支持的人，”他说。 “因为她的礼物太稀有了。她的天赋与她的悲情有很大关系。她令人难以置信的歌唱天赋直击她的内心。这在歌手中是很少见的。大多数歌手都是演员。西妮德不是演员。”</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wax-museum-apologise-and-remove-sinead-oconnor-figure-after-backlash-we-can-do-better-3778364">都柏林一家蜡像馆在强烈反对后道歉并移除了西妮德·奥康纳的雕像。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnors-exact-cause-of-death-revealed-one-year-after-death-3778624">西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor) 去世一年后透露的确切死因</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
